{"tid":2275651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽講四年後彭斯，蓬佩奧上台撥亂反正，滅共","createTime":"2020-11-07T10:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T10:49:58.000Z","uid":52265,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a72a501f578ddd53cf26dd45469e5adb5294db3","tid":2275651,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"1946,年，白崇禧指揮國軍擊敗林彪領導的東北民主聯軍，國軍取得第二次四平戰役勝利，直下長春。白主張乘勝追擊，一舉殲滅林彪所部中共軍，但由於美國總統特使喬治&middot;卡特萊特&middot;馬歇爾連續三次給蔣發電，並以斷絕美援相威脅，迫蔣停止在東北的軍事行動；同時，前方國軍總指揮杜聿明向南京請示，蔣遂電令杜「暫緩追擊」。此舉使林彪殘部得以喘息，導致東北大局逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------<br />\n<br />\n仲有一單叫西安事變<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523093e3218d8a5d2bdeaaf73c68fdf87fb2d031","tid":2275651,"uid":222614,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:18:24.000Z","msg":"如果選舉舞弊都畀佢地過到骨<br />\n<br />\n唔洗諗再有 trump呢類真反派可以有機會上場喇"},{"pid":"f097ce22c3fe38f779d9f3c64eede0044cdf13a4","tid":2275651,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"停戰令根本痴線,不過之後美軍要係韓戰越戰幫杜魯門還命"},{"pid":"c4160ce927441ec899717c644b1ca04d80692fea","tid":2275651,"uid":52265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:18:41.000Z","msg":"歷史就係咁，老共好命到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7903ec2a63be004577ab6cef36a7c58d65732ab7","tid":2275651,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"睇返歷史八成奶共動作都係民主黨做出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfe31a7b9308956f5060acea3ebd8b0d6199e94","tid":2275651,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4160ce927441ec899717c644b1ca04d80692fea","tid":2275651,"uid":52265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202